Usage: CDCC REQUEST text|OFF
  Tells leechers what you need

  Just pass it what you'd like leechers to send to you and whenever client
  receives SEND request, it will send them notice saying what you need.

See also:
  CDCC OFFER
  CDCC DOFFER
  CDCC PSEND
  CDCC LIST
  CDCC PLIST
  CDCC LOAD
  CDCC SAVE
